init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien has been watching Matt Damon movies and has mistaken him for a hero.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is reluctant to help, but the alien has kidnapped his wife, so he has no choice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He eventually finds the enemy base and starts shooting.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon is confused, but he signs them anyway.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are hanging on his every word.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens thank him for his help and he's happy to have helped.
